# Tailwind CSS v4 (current)

This project targets **Tailwind CSS v4.x** (latest: v4.3). Do **not** generate v3 config or APIs unless explicitly migrating legacy code.

References: [Upgrade guide](https://tailwindcss.com/docs/upgrade-guide), [v4.3 blog](https://tailwindcss.com/blog/tailwindcss-v4-3)

## Setup (v4, not v3)

```css
/* globals.css — correct */
@import "tailwindcss";

/* ❌ v3 — never add these */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
```

```js
// postcss.config.mjs — correct
export default { plugins: { "@tailwindcss/postcss": {} } };

// ❌ v3 — remove tailwindcss, postcss-import, autoprefixer from plugins
```

- PostCSS plugin package is **`@tailwindcss/postcss`**, not `tailwindcss`.
- Next.js/webpack: prefer **`@tailwindcss/webpack`** loader over PostCSS for ~2× faster builds (v4.2+).
- Vite: use **`@tailwindcss/vite`**. CLI: **`@tailwindcss/cli`**.
- **`tailwind.config.js` is not auto-loaded.** Theme lives in CSS via `@theme`. Load JS config only if needed: `@config "./tailwind.config.js"`.
- No `content: []` array — v4 scans sources automatically. Use `@source` to add paths.
- Install: `npm install tailwindcss@latest @tailwindcss/postcss@latest`

## Theme and custom CSS (CSS-first)

```css
@theme {
  --color-brand: oklch(0.55 0.2 250);
  --font-sans: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
}

/* shadcn/ui v4: map semantic tokens in @theme inline { ... } */
```

- Prefer **`var(--color-red-500)`** over `theme(colors.red.500)` in custom CSS.
- Custom component classes: use **`@utility`**, not `@layer utilities` / `@layer components`.
- Custom `container`: extend with `@utility container { ... }` (v3 `theme.container` options removed).
- Sass/Less/Stylus: **not supported** with v4. Use plain CSS.
- Vue/Svelte/CSS modules using `@apply`: add **`@reference`** to the main CSS file.

## v3 → v4 breaking changes agents get wrong

| Wrong (v3) | Correct (v4) |
|------------|--------------|
| `shadow-sm` (same visual) | `shadow-xs` |
| `shadow` | `shadow-sm` |
| `rounded-sm` | `rounded-xs` |
| `outline-none` (invisible outline) | `outline-hidden` |
| `outline-none` (no outline) | `outline-none` |
| `ring` (3px blue) | `ring-3 ring-blue-500` (defaults: 1px, `currentColor`) |
| `bg-opacity-50` | `bg-black/50` |
| `flex-grow-*` / `flex-shrink-*` | `grow-*` / `shrink-*` |
| `bg-[--var]` | `bg-(--var)` |
| `!flex` / `hover:!bg-red-500` | `flex!` / `hover:bg-red-500!` |
| `transform-none` to reset scale/rotate | `scale-none`, `rotate-none`, etc. |
| `grid-cols-[a,b]` (comma = space) | `grid-cols-[a_b]` (underscore = space) |
| Variant order `first:*:pt-0` | `*:first:pt-0` (left-to-right in v4) |
| `bg-gradient-to-r` | `bg-linear-to-r` (gradient variant behavior changed) |

**Defaults changed:** borders/divides use `currentColor` (add explicit `border-gray-200` if needed). Buttons use `cursor: default`. `space-x/y` and `divide-x/y` selectors changed — prefer **`gap`** on flex/grid.

**Browser floor:** Safari 16.4+, Chrome 111+, Firefox 128+. Use v3.4 only if older browsers are required.

## v4.2 additions

- **Palettes:** `mauve`, `olive`, `mist`, `taupe` (neutral alternatives to gray/slate/zinc).
- **Logical properties:** `pbs-*`/`pbe-*`, `mbs-*`/`mbe-*`, `inline-*`/`block-*`, `inset-s-*`/`inset-e-*`/`inset-bs-*`/`inset-be-*`. Prefer over deprecated `start-*`/`end-*`.
- **`font-features-*`:** OpenType settings; prefer `tabular-nums` for tabular figures.

## v4.3 additions

- **Scrollbars:** `scrollbar-auto` \| `scrollbar-thin` \| `scrollbar-none`; `scrollbar-thumb-*`, `scrollbar-track-*`; `scrollbar-gutter-stable`.
- **Size containers:** `@container-size` (not just `@container` inline-size) for `cqb`/`cqh` units.
- **`zoom-*`:** CSS `zoom` property (`zoom-75`, `zoom-[1.1]`, `zoom-(--var)`).
- **`tab-*`:** `tab-size` for `<pre>`/code (`tab-2`, bare `tab` defaults to 4 in v4.3).
- **`@variant` in CSS:** stacked (`@variant hover:focus { }`) and compound (`@variant hover, focus { }`).
- **Functional `@utility`:** `--default(...)` for utilities that work with or without a value.

## shadcn/ui with Tailwind v4

- Init with v4-compatible style (e.g. **`new-york-v4`** in `components.json`).
- Animations: import **`tw-animate-css`**, not `tailwindcss-animate` plugin.
- Components live in `components/ui/`; use `cn()` from `lib/utils.ts`.

## Agent checklist

Before suggesting Tailwind changes, verify:

1. Using `@import "tailwindcss"` and `@tailwindcss/postcss` (or webpack/vite plugin)?
2. Theme/extensions in `@theme` / `@utility`, not `tailwind.config.js` `extend`?
3. Utility class names match **v4** renamed scale (shadow/rounded/blur)?
4. Not reintroducing v3-only plugins (`autoprefixer`, `tailwindcss-animate`)?
5. For Next.js in this repo: changes go in **`apps/web/`**.
